Project Name: InboxIQ

Description:
InboxIQ is an AI-powered smart email assistant that sits on top of Gmail rather than replacing it.

Tech Stack:
- Flask backend
- SQLite initially
- Gmail API
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript frontend
- Scikit-Learn for ML

Architecture Rules:
- Business logic goes in services/
- Routes should remain thin.
- ML code lives in app/ml/
- Gmail API logic lives in gmail_service.py
- Environment variables go in .env
- Prefer clean, modular code.

Project Goal:
Build a production-quality project suitable for SDE internships where ML is only a component of the application rather than the entire application.

Current Milestone:
Create a minimal Flask application that starts successfully and serves a homepage.